## ğŸ’¡ Features

  

- ğŸ« **Guest Entry Form**: Visitors can enter their **name**, **agency**, **email**, and a brief **description**.

- ğŸ“‹ **Admin Dashboard**: Admins can view and manage all guest entries.

- ğŸ§± **Database Integration**: All data is stored in a MySQL database using Spring JPA.

- ğŸ’» **MVC Pattern**: The project follows the Model-View-Controller architecture for clean and maintainable code.

  

## ğŸ¯ Purpose

  

The purpose of this project was to:

